com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants

Class CKF

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CKF

  • public class CKF
extends java.lang.Object
    Class defining Cryptoki CKF_ constants - Bit Flags.

    Further information concerning the various flag values is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
